      "updated": 1772624370051,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"When the question implies\n a comparison, ranking, or\n distribution, append a\n fenced ```chart``` block:\n\n {\n   chart_type: bar|line|pie,\n   title: \"...\",\n   x_key: \"name\",\n   y_key: \"value\",\n   data: [\n     {name, value}, ...\n   ]\n }\n\n to your natural-language\n answer.\"",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"When the question implies\n a comparison, ranking, or\n distribution, append a\n fenced ```chart``` block:\n\n {\n   chart_type: bar|line|pie,\n   title: \"...\",\n   x_key: \"name\",\n   y_key: \"value\",\n   data: [\n     {name, value}, ...\n   ]\n }\n\n to your natural-language\n answer.\"",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
